{"tid":1805863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你覺得好似得自己作戰，入嚟睇條片","createTime":"2020-01-01T01:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T02:05:55.000Z","uid":293998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad74a5114ae72c5f66032808278c8589dfdd7498","tid":1805863,"uid":293998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T01:58:26.000Z","msg":"2020，又係一個新嘅開始。<br />\n經歷咗半年大家都攰了，<br />\n尤其是去到依家<br />\n好似少咗好多國際新聞關於香港咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為為台灣線其中一份子，<br />\n我地有時都會覺得推唔起好多野，<br />\n無啲咩實際作用幫手喺香港打生打死嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但，WE ARE NOT ALONE</span></span><br />\n有好多台灣人已經開始會自己搞一啲活動<br />\n去將香港嘅抗戰精神，慢慢咁滲落去自己嘅生活圈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">以下條片只係其中好少好少部份嘅台灣人<br />\n其實仲有好多唔同地方嘅台灣人默默咁支持我地</span><br />\n<br />\n片尾嘅相其實係真係台灣人自己過嚟影<br />\n希望可以show 到support比大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1CdMTn0uba3P8qGy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1CdMTn0uba3P8qGy&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=21eb4448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1CdMTn0uba3P8qGy</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4t7S7ma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4t7S7ma.jpg&h=2726525c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，依家搞緊嘅和你寫<br />\n我地都收到起碼<span style=\"color: gold;\">幾百張台灣人親手寫嘅卡</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">全部都陸續寄返香港，會用唔同方法比到手足們</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OxJCyY1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxJCyY1.jpg&h=aa5072d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿忘手足，堅守初衷<br />\n2020，我地重新出發<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"548d5a4f086abec86c3380646cd2b33b1dce9586","tid":1805863,"uid":293998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T01:58:49.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n勿忘手足，堅守初衷<br />\n2020，我地重新出發<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"2087217c8dedf03094d5feb41444462742a76474","tid":1805863,"uid":293998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62671a5b911202b93ecd5980b7c9e03afca7f250","tid":1805863,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝喺台灣努力嘅手足"},{"pid":"608b88bf08c1d2f6ee55a458c0f09c90423d426e","tid":1805863,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d21wDuL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd21wDuL.jpg&h=ac282777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zfA9p9M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzfA9p9M.jpg&h=fd5272ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzFUBgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzFUBgr.jpg&h=bc595c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPEY2Ws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPEY2Ws.jpg&h=c25e03a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DFMD2Wt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDFMD2Wt.jpg&h=8ab1bfe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGd7bPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGd7bPO.jpg&h=1804c54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drLA49P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai